'''以馬內利非裔衛理公會教堂'''（{{lang-en|Emanuel African Methodist Episcopal Church}}）位於[[美國|美國]][[南卡羅萊納州|南卡羅萊納州]][[查爾斯頓_(南卡羅萊納州)|查爾斯頓]]，始建於1816年。是美國[[非裔衛理公會|非裔衛理公會]]在[[美國南部|美國南部]]最古老的教堂。堂內信眾團體也是[[巴爾的摩|巴爾的摩]]以南最古老的。

2015年6月17日，教堂遭受[[2015年南卡羅萊納州查爾斯頓槍擊案|槍擊]]。<ref name=WashingtonPost-Shooting-2015>{{cite news |last1=Bever |first1=Lindsey |last2=Costa |first2=Robert |script-title=en:9 dead in shooting at historic Charleston African American church. Police chief calls it ‘hate crime.’ |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/06/17/white-gunman-sought-in-shooting-at-historic-charleston-african-ame-church/ |accessdate=18 June 2015 |work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |date=17 June 2015 |archive-date=2019-05-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509205857/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/06/17/white-gunman-sought-in-shooting-at-historic-charleston-african-ame-church/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>九人死亡，其中一人是州參議員[[克萊門塔·平克尼|克萊門塔·平克尼]]牧師。<ref name=NBCNews-Shooting-2015>{{cite news |last1 = Johnson |first1 = M. Alex |title = 'This Was a Hate Crime': Nine People Killed at Historic South Carolina Church |url = http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/multiple-people-shot-historic-south-carolina-church-n377436 |accessdate = 18 June 2015 |work = [[NBC_News|NBC News]] |date = 17 June 2015 |archive-date = 2017-11-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171107112944/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/multiple-people-shot-historic-south-carolina-church-n377436 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

